title: Team O'Neill benelux -- Sal Puro do Oeste
description: Four O'Neill Benelux Team riders went on a surftrip to discover the good waves, beautiful places and faces of the Oeste Region of Portugal. They discovered it all: good waves all week long, castles, culture, wine and even got a chance to see O'Neill's Jordy Smith doing his thing at the Moche Pro! Check out why Portugal should be your next surftrip destination!
